Creating FTP Folder

1. Mounting ISO file
cd to directory where file is located
	# mount -o loop FILENAME.iso /directory/of/file
to unmount a loop
	# umount -d FILENAME.iso

2. Install and configure Apache Server
	# yum -y install httpd
	# systemctl start httpd
	# systemctl enable httpd

3. Verify the Apache Server is enabled and running properly
in a web browser, navigate to 127.0.0.1/directory/of/mounted/file
A page showing the server is running properly will display

** Port 80 must be open in the firewall **
